<ab facs="#facs_84_r3l23">Jm cʒugehoren <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> / Nu hat der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor vns cʒu den <expan>heıl<ex>igen</ex></expan> </ab>
