<ab facs="#facs_84_r3l25">des von hohenloch niht / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ſıe ledig <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
